-- Northwest Airlines to Plead Guilty, Pay Fine on Price Fixing
-- Phil Kohn
-- 2010-07-30T17:57:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-30/northwest-airlines-to-plead-guilty-pay-38-million-in-cargo-pricing-case.html

          
          
             Northwest Airlines LLC has agreed to
plead guilty and to pay a $38 million criminal fine for its
role, through Northwest Airlines Cargo, in a conspiracy to fix
prices in the air transportation industry, the U.S. Department
of Justice said today in an e-mailed statement.  
          
          


  


        